01:00:04.830 --> 01:00:07.070
women writers in the '80s and '90s.

01:00:07.070 --> 01:00:10.670
Hilderaz [assumed spelling] was
a great advocate and made space

01:00:10.670 --> 01:00:15.080
for women's writing, where, very
often, most of the other journals,

01:00:15.080 --> 01:00:17.760
which were run by dudes, were
not doing that kind of work.

01:00:17.760 --> 01:00:21.890
And some of our great poets
today, who we know by name,

01:00:21.890 --> 01:00:25.300
