groups and the poets writing

01:10:27.670 --> 01:10:31.770
in those languages have a life
beyond their language groups

01:10:31.770 --> 01:10:33.740
and their communities
and have a life beyond

01:10:33.740 --> 01:10:35.260
that through translation.

01:10:35.260 --> 01:10:39.820
And I think that's
an important thing.

01:10:39.820 --> 01:10:42.000
The other things is that I also
know that there's a lot of work

01:10:42.000 --> 01:10:44.480
in those countries, more
work in those countries,

01:10:44.480 --> 01:10:49.350
in preserving those language group
publications than, for instance,

01:10:49.350 --> 01:10:51.010
in just publishing poets.

01:10:51.010 --> 01:10:55.500 position:56%
They would publish a language group
work rather than just publish a poet

01:10:55.500 --> 01:10:57.300
for the sake of publishing a poet.

01:10:57.300 --> 01:10:59.000
And this is true in India as well.

01:10:59.000 --> 01:11:01.710
I mean, if you -- one
of the fantastic things

01:11:01.710 --> 01:11:05.310
about India is they're such
a wide publishing world

01:11:05.310 --> 01:11:09.220
in the different Indian languages
that has created a great thing.

01:11:09.220 --> 01:11:11.410
But of course, their
survival, as they say,

01:11:11.410 --> 01:11:14.880
always is if the work
is not translated,

01:11:14.880 --> 01:11:16.720
we don't get the attention
and so on.

01:11:16.720 --> 01:11:18.910
So we limit -- we are limited.

01:11:18.910 --> 01:11:22.220
We intentionally limit what we can
do to make sure things can be done.

01:11:22.220 --> 01:11:24.450
And so, one of the things that
we want to do is pay attention

01:11:24.450 --> 01:11:27.350
to translation as a
big part of our work.

01:11:27.350 --> 01:11:29.060
Yeah.

01:11:29.060 --> 01:11:32.540
&gt;&gt; My name is William [inaudible].

01:11:32.540 --> 01:11:33.840
&gt;&gt; Kwame Dawes: Yes.

01:11:33.840 --> 01:11:35.870
&gt;&gt; And I'm from Guyana, too.

01:11:35.870 --> 01:11:37.170
I'm from [inaudible].

01:11:37.170 --> 01:11:45.150
In this -- with the question
she asked, I want to find

01:11:45.150 --> 01:11:51.660
out if you think it would be proper
